OK, I'm not sure if this is in the right area, but this is the most fitting one I found. So, I saw this black and white checkerboard pattern tank that I can't find the mod it's from. So, anyone know what mod it's from? I downloaded KW Rocketry, NovaPunch, and AIES Aerospace, and it's not in any of those.
